12:30 uzirinde gushukwa ukabakurikiza, nibamara kurimburwa imbere yawe. Ntuzabaririze iby'imana zabo uti “Ya mahanga yakoreraga imana zayo ate? Nanjye ndabigenza ntyo.”
12:31 Ntuzagirire Uwiteka Imana yawe nka bo, kuko ikintu cyose Uwiteka yita ikizira akacyanga urunuka bagikorera imana zabo, ndetse n'abahungu babo n'abakobwa babo babosereze imana zabo.
13:1  Icyo mbategeka cyose mujye mucyitondera mucyumvire, ntimukacyongereho, ntimukakigabanyeho.
13:2 Muri mwe nihaboneka umuhanuzi cyangwa umurōsi, akakubwira ikimenyetso cyangwa igitangaza,
13:3 icyo kimenyetso cyangwa icyo gitangaza kigasohora, icyo yakubwiye agira ati “Duhindukirire izindi mana izo utigeze kumenya tuzikorere”,
13:4 ntuzemere amagambo y'uwo muhanuzi cyangwa y'uwo murōsi, kuko Uwiteka Imana yanyu izaba ibagerageza, ngo imenye yuko mukundisha Uwiteka Imana yanyu imitima yanyu yose n'ubugingo bwanyu bwose.
13:5 Ahubwo mujye muyoborwa n'Uwiteka Imana yanyu muyubahe, mwitondere amategeko yayo muyumvire, muyikorere muyifatanyeho akaramata.
13:6 Kandi uwo muhanuzi cyangwa uwo murōsi bazamwicire kuko azaba avuze ibyo kubagomeshereza Uwiteka Imana yanyu, yabakuye mu gihugu cya Egiputa ikabacungura mu nzu y'uburetwa, n'ibyo kubatesha inzira Uwiteka Imana yanyu yabategetse gucamo, abe ari ko mukura ikibi hagati muri mwe.
13:7 Mwene nyoko cyangwa umuhungu wawe cyangwa umukobwa wawe, cyangwa umugore useguye cyangwa incuti yawe y'amagara, yakoshya rwihishwa ati “Tugende dukorere izindi mana” (utigeze kumenya, na ba sekuruza banyu batigeze kumenya,
13:8 zo mu mana z'amahanga abagose, ari hafi yanyu cyangwa abari kure, ahereye ku mpera y'isi akageza ku yindi mpera yayo),
13:9 ntuzamwemerere, ntuzamwumvire, ntuzamubabarire, ntuzamukize, ntuzamuhishīre,
13:10 ahubwo ntuzabure kumwica. Ukuboko kwawe abe ari ko kubanza kumwica, maze habone gukuriraho n'abandi bantu bose.
13:11 Uzamwicishirize amabuye, kuko yagerageje kugushukashuka ngo agukure ku Uwiteka Imana yawe, yagukuye mu gihugu cya Egiputa mu nzu y'uburetwa.
13:12 Abisirayeli bose bazabyumva batinye, be kongera gukorera ikibi kingana gityo hagati muri mwe.
13:13 Wakumva inkuru y'umwe mu midugudu yawe Uwiteka Imana yawe iguha guturamo, bavuga bati
13:14 “Hari ibigoryi byaturutse hagati muri mwe bishukashuka abo mu mudugudu wabo biti ‘Tugende dukorere izindi mana mutigeze kumenya’ ”,
13:15 uzabibaririze, ubishakishe ubigenzure. Nusanga ari iby'ukuri bidashidikanywa yuko ikizira kingana gityo gikorerwa hagati muri mwe,
13:16 ntuzabure kwicisha abo muri uwo mudugudu inkota, uwurimburane rwose n'ibirimo byose, urimburishe amatungo yawo inkota.
13:17 Isahu yawo uyiteranirize hagati mu nzira yawo, uwutwikane n'isahu yawo yose imbere y'Uwiteka Imana yawe, uwo mudugudu uzabe ikirundo cy'ibyashenywe iteka, ntukubakwe ukundi.
13:18 Ntukagire icyo ugundira mu byashinganywe kugira ngo Uwiteka arakuruke uburakari bwe bugurumana, akubabarire akugirire ibambe, akugwize nk'uko yarahiye ba sekuruza banyu,
13:19 abitewe n'uko wumviye Uwiteka Imana yawe, ukitondera amategeko yayo yose ngutegeka uyu munsi, ugakora ibyo Uwiteka Imana yawe ibona ko ari byiza.
14:1  Muri abana b'Uwiteka Imana yanyu, ntimukiraburishe kwikeba ku mubiri, haba no kwitegera ibiharanjongo uwapfuye.
14:2  Kuko uri ubwoko bwerejwe Uwiteka Imana yawe, kandi Uwiteka akagutoraniriza mu mahanga yose yo mu isi kuba ubwoko yironkeye.
14:3  Ntukarye ikintu cyose kizira.
14:4 Aya ni yo matungo n'inyamaswa mwemererwa kurya: inka n'intama n'ihene,
14:5 n'impara n'isirabo n'isunu, n'impongo n'inyemera n'ifumbēri n'itwiga.
14:6 Mu nyamaswa n'amatungo, icyatuye inzara cyose ngo kigire imigeri igabanije kikūza, abe ari cyo mujya murya.
14:7 Ariko ibi ntimukabirye mu byūza no mu byatuye inzara: ingamiya n'urukwavu n'impereryi, kuko byūza bikaba bitatuye inzara, ni ibihumanya kuri mwe.
14:8 N'ingurube kuko yatuye inzara ariko ntiyūze, ni igihumanya kuri mwe. Inyama zazo ntimukazirye, n'intumbi zazo ntimukazikoreho.
14:9 Ibi abe ari byo mujya murya mu byo mu mazi byose: igifite amababa n'ibikoko cyose mujye mukirya,
14:10 ikidafite amababa n'ibikoko cyose ntimukakirye, ni igihumanya kuri mwe.
14:11 Ibisiga n'inyoni bidahumanya byose mwemererwa kubirya.
14:12 Ariko ibi ntimukabirye: ikizu n'itanangabo na oziniya,
14:13 n'inkongoro y'impimakazi, n'icyarūzi n'icyanira uko amoko yabyo ari,
14:14 n'igikōna cyose uko amoko yabyo ari,
14:15 na mbuni na tamasi, na shakafu n'agaca n'ibyo mu bwoko bwako byose,
14:16 n'igihunyira gito n'igihunyira kinini n'igihunyira cy'amatwi,
14:17 n'inzoya n'inkongoro na sarumpfuna,
14:18 n'igishondabagabo n'uruyongoyongo uko amoko yazo ari, n'inkotsa n'agacurama.
14:19 Ibigira amababa bikagenza amaguru magufi byose, ni ibihumanya kuri mwe ntimukabirye.
14:20 Mwemererwa kurya ibisiga n'inyoni bidahumanya byose.
14:21   Ntimukarye intumbyi yose. Wemererwa kuyiha umusuhuke w'umunyamahanga uri iwanyu akayirya, cyangwa wemererwa kuyigurisha umunyamahanga. Wehoho uri ubwoko bwerejwe Uwiteka Imana yawe. Ntugatekeshe umwana w'ihene amahenehene ya nyina.
14:22   Ntuzabure gutanga kimwe mu icumi cy'imyaka yose iva ku mbuto wabibye, iyo imirima yawe izera uko umwaka utashye.
14:23 Kandi uzajye urīra imbere y'Uwiteka Imana yawe, ahantu izatoraniriza kuhashyira izina ryayo ngo rihabe, kimwe mu icumi cy'amasaka yawe n'icya vino yawe, n'icy'amavuta ya elayo yawe, n'uburiza bw'amashyo yawe n'ubw'imikumbi yawe, kugira ngo wige guhora wubaha Uwiteka Imana yawe iteka.
14:24 Ahari Uwiteka Imana yawe nimara kuguha umugisha, urugendo rwakunanira ntubashe kujyana ibyo, kuko ahantu Uwiteka Imana yawe izaba yaratoranirije kuhashyira izina ryayo hakubaye kure.
14:25 Nibimera bityo uzabigure ifeza, uzihambire uzijyane, ujye ahantu Uwiteka Imana yawe izaba yaratoranije,
14:26 uziguremo icyo ushaka cyose: inka cyangwa intama cyangwa vino cyangwa igisindisha, cyangwa ikindi cyose umutima wawe ushaka, ubisangirire n'abo mu rugo rwawe aho hantu imbere y'Uwiteka Imana yawe, mwishimane,
14:27 kandi ubisangire n'Umulewi w'iwanyu, ntukamurangarane kuko adafite umugabane cyangwa gakondo muri mwe.
14:28 Uko imyaka itatu ishize, uzajye ukuraho kimwe mu icumi cy'imyaka yose wejeje muri uwo mwaka, ubibike iwanyu.
14:29 Maze Umulewi kuko adafite umugabane cyangwa gakondo muri mwe, n'umusuhuke w'umunyamahanga, n'impfubyi n'umupfakazi bari iwanyu bazaze barye bahage, kugira ngo Uwiteka Imana yawe iguhere umugisha imirimo ukora yose.
15:1 Uko imyaka irindwi ishize, uzajye ugira ibyo uhara.
15:2 Ubu abe ari bwo buba uburyo bw'uko guhara: umwishyuza wese aharire mugenzi we icyo yamugurije, ntazacyishyuze mugenzi we na mwene wabo, kuko guhara kwategetswe n'Uwiteka kwaranzwe.
15:3 Wemererwa kwishyuza umunyamahanga, ariko icyawe cyose gifitwe na mwene wanyu, uzakimuharire.
15:4 Ariko ntihazagire abakene baba muri mwe, kuko Uwiteka atazabura kuguhera umugisha mu gihugu Uwiteka Imana yawe iguha ho gakondo ngo ugihindūre,
15:5 niba ugira umwete wo kumvira Uwiteka Imana yawe, ngo witondere aya mategeko yose ngutegeka uyu munsi, uyumvire.
15:6 Kuko Uwiteka Imana yawe izaguha umugisha nk'uko yagusezeranije, kandi uzaguriza amahanga menshi ariko ntuzayaguzaho, kandi uzatwara amahanga menshi ariko yo ntazagutwara.
15:7   Nihaba muri mwe umukene ari umwe muri bene wanyu, ahantu hose h'iwanyu mu gihugu Uwiteka Imana yawe iguha, ntuzanangire umutima wawe, ntuzagundire ibyawe ngo ubyime mwene wanyu w'umukene,
15:8 ahubwo ntuzabure kumuramburira iminwe, ntuzabure kumuguriza ibimumaze ubukene bw'icyo akeneye.
15:9 Wirinde kwibwira icy'ubuntu buke uti “Umwaka wa karindwi wo guhara imyenda urenda gutaha”, bigatuma urebana imbabazi nke mwene wanyu w'umukene ukanga kugira icyo umuha, adatakira Uwiteka akurega, ukagibwaho n'icyaha.
15:10 Ntuzabure kumuha kandi numuha ntibizakubabaze, kuko icyo ngicyo kizatuma Uwiteka Imana yawe iguhera umugisha umurimo wawe wose, n'ibyo ugerageza gukora byose.
15:11  Kuko ari ntabwo abakene bazashira mu gihugu, ni cyo gitumye ngutegeka nti “Ntuzabure kuramburira iminwe mwene wanyu w'umukene w'umworo uri mu gihugu cyawe.”
15:12   Nibakugurisha mwene wanyu w'Umuheburayo cyangwa w'Umuheburayokazi akagukorera imyaka itandatu, mu wa karindwi uzamuhare ngo akuveho, agire umudendezo.
15:13 Kandi numuhara ngo agende agire umudendezo, ntuzamuhare nta cyo umuhaye,
15:14 ahubwo uzamuhe byinshi ku mukumbi wawe, no ku mbuga yawe uhuriraho, no ku muvure wawe wengeramo vino, uko Uwiteka Imana yawe yaguhaye umugisha, azabe ari ko umuha.
15:15 Uzibuke yuko nawe wari umuretwa mu gihugu cya Egiputa Uwiteka Imana yawe ikagucungura, ni cyo gitumye uyu munsi ngutegeka ibyo.
15:16 Kandi nakubwira ati “Sinshaka kukuvaho”, kuko agukunda n'abo mu rugo rwawe akamerana neza nawe,
15:17 uzende uruhindu urumupfumuze ugutwi rusohoke ku rugi, maze agumye kuba imbata yawe iteka. N'umuja wawe uzamugenze utyo.
15:18 Numuhara ngo akuveho, agire umudendezo, ntibizagutere agahinda kuko yagukoreye imyaka itandatu, ukaba umuhembye igice cya kabiri cy'ibihembo wari ukwiriye guhemba umukozi ubikorera, kandi Uwiteka Imana yawe izaguhera umugisha ibyo ukora byose.
15:19   Uburiza bw'ikigabo bwose bwo mu mashyo yawe no mu mikumbi yawe, uzajye ubwereza Uwiteka Imana yawe. Ntugakoreshe uburiza bw'inka yawe, ntukogoshe uburiza bwo mu mukumbi wawe.
15:20 Ujye ubusangirira n'abo mu rugo rwawe imbere y'Uwiteka Imana yawe uko umwaka utashye, ahantu Uwiteka azatoranya.
15:21 Nibugira inenge yose, nibucumbagira cyangwa nibuhuma, cyangwa nibugira indi nenge mbi yose, ntuzabutambire Uwiteka Imana yawe.
15:22 Uzaburīre iwanyu, uhumanye n'udahumanye bahwanye kuburya nk'uko barya isirabo n'impara.
15:23  Ariko ntuzarye amaraso yabwo, ahubwo uzajye uyavushiriza hasi nk'uko bamena amazi.
